{"tid":1930253,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★意大利超市搶剩菠蘿Pizza　意大利網民：我們可能死但仍有尊嚴","createTime":"2020-03-17T12:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T12:40:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"45f8599d15bf6524d0552f330091d6217f8e3d50","tid":1930253,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"意大利人堅持正宗的 pizza 不應該加菠蘿作配料，正如源自意大利的拿坡里 pizza，經典口味只會利用番茄、水牛芝士、新鮮羅勒和橄欖油製作。很多意大利人看到有菠蘿的 pizza 都很少食用，他們會很不滿意，甚至感到憤怒。<br />\n<br />\n這樣就難怪在意大利的超級市場內，仍然看到這款 pizza 的存貨，原來有菠蘿的 pizza 在當地並不受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/ETE1RbHWAAEEGzM.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F03%2FETE1RbHWAAEEGzM.jpeg&h=5326e91d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/03/17/nopineappleonpizza/hottopic/food/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F03%2F17%2Fnopineappleonpizza%2Fhottopic%2Ffood%2F&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB9qeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=19f5900c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/03/17/nopineappleonpizza/hottopic/food/</a>"},{"pid":"2fa18ad824301e6f9e603bb7638869b582ef76ab","tid":1930253,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"腦魔有冇去老麥執2手薯條食"},{"pid":"d55a128c98bba062e5e5ff3be1fdcde271829fe7","tid":1930253,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fa18ad824301e6f9e603bb7638869b582ef76ab","tid":1930253,"uid":29080,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"腦魔有冇去老麥執2手薯條食"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:05:30.000Z","msg":"no<br />\n<br />\nvery few人"},{"pid":"b65d02d9040bfe1f66ac5dafe5144d6a89f82de1","tid":1930253,"uid":41545,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"其實加菠蘿好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"h